    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend trip, it runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
