    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a quintessential analog performer. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of this chassis. While the finish shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' designation, the drivetrain is robust and track-ready. A purist\u2019s spec designed for the driver who prioritizes kinetic performance over showroom aesthetics.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
