    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and reliable performance. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road-wear expected of a carefully driven car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show minimal wear, while all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having followed a strict service schedule with recent oil changes and a comprehensive brake inspection. The tires offer plenty of tread for the seasons ahead. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key vehicle for a buyer who values both aesthetic appeal and mechanical peace of mind.",
