    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved and looked after, showing just the normal signs of being a dependable daily driver. It\u2019s the perfect pick if you\u2019re looking for something reliable and fun to drive without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m super happy to answer any questions you have, so don\u2019t be shy\u2014let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
