    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with its signature high-revving character and individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain is optimized by a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure for this platform. Suspension geometry utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, providing exceptional lateral grip and feedback. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, ready for the apex.",
